  </div>
  <div class="company-line"><span class="company">DreamWorks Animation</span> &middot; Glendale, CA</div>
  <ul>
    <li>Worked on hair and cloth simulation across Houdini and Maya pipelines on films including <em>Puss in Boots</em> and <em>Turbo</em>.</li>
    <li>Built out toolsets supporting character effects artists in production.</li>
  </ul>
